{"tid":350715,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人有流星雨觀賞經驗？","createTime":"2017-08-07T12:38:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-10T17:54:33.000Z","uid":63639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cfdf660011fb5b565e25c8aacb2b94f481307fcd","tid":350715,"uid":63639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T12:38:47.000Z","msg":"星期六有英仙座流星雨，想帶個女仔去一齊睇，有冇巴絲打有經驗可以講一講有咩要注意，同埋有咩合適地點推介？<br />\n<br />\n萬宜水庫好似太煩，因為要行好遠路，個女仔可能頂唔順。"},{"pid":"ec2acefe5cce1ef8c9952d80cb8a0637123ce09e","tid":350715,"uid":68231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T12:39:34.000Z","msg":"我都想知呀"},{"pid":"b1889769e9b25ff776c10a4cd1cd267e780b8a22","tid":350715,"uid":63639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T12:40:25.000Z","msg":"Hk01 報導<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2wqJT38\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2wqJT38&d=lh8eEwqKkF3ilPH2M05HX7r9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=b96ee17f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2wqJT38</a>"},{"pid":"27776ec7c8b4bf701896d826a361130caec38aa4","tid":350715,"uid":34612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T00:22:34.000Z","msg":"長洲梅窩睇唔睇到？"},{"pid":"9dfcaba33eddb3deaaa6acb32591ed11806348bf","tid":350715,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T00:25:21.000Z","msg":"不過根據天文台的天氣預測，當日天氣短暫時間有陽光，有幾陣驟雨，或會影響觀賞流星雨。余惠俊指天氣相當影響觀星機會，因流星需與空氣摩擦才能產生光，惟有雲遮擋就難以觀看。<br />\n<br />\n天文匯主席彭栩怡就指去年適逢天氣欠佳，未能觀看成功，最近一次觀看英仙座流星雨已是大約10年前：「如天文台表示天氣唔理想，市民都不宜期望太高。」"},{"pid":"909208a12d1d80a6d4c03ec1d70b92c00211b1b6","tid":350715,"uid":86651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T17:54:33.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推，同女朋友都去睇"}]}